    SELECT TOP(1) [t].[Id], [t].[CountOfQuestions], [t].[CreatedAt], [t].[IsPrivate], [t].[IsRandom], [t].[Name], [t].[TestType], [t].[TimeLimitMinutes], [t].[TopicId], [t0].[Id] AS [Id0], [t0].[CategoryId], [t0].[Name] AS [Name0]

) AS [s]
